{"word":"G4634 - σκηνοπηγία - skēnopēgía - skay-nop-ayg-ee'-ah - Tabernacles","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σκηνοπηγία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">skēnopēgía</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">skay-nop-ayg-ee'-ah</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Tabernacles</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"கூடாரம் - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. the construction of a tabernacle"},{"paragraph":"2. the feast of tabernacles"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4636 - σκῆνος - skēnos - skay'-nos/4636\">G4636</a> and <a href=\"#/G4078 - πήγνυμι - pḗgnymi - payg'-noo-mee/4078\">G4078</a>; the <i>Festival of Tabernacles</i> (so called from the custom of erecting booths for temporary homes): - tabernacles.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1981/1981\">G1981</a>, <a href=\"#/G2681/2681\">G2681</a>, <a href=\"#/G4633/4633\">G4633</a>, <a href=\"#/G4634/4634\">G4634</a>, <a href=\"#/G4635/4635\">G4635</a>, <a href=\"#/G4636/4636\">G4636</a>, <a href=\"#/G4637/4637\">G4637</a>, <a href=\"#/G4638/4638\">G4638</a>"}]}